<item>
            <title>[CAMEL-16874] PollEnrich with file and option sendEmptyMessageWhenIdle keeps sending empty messages</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CAMEL-16874</link>
                <project id="12311211" key="CAMEL">Camel</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In &lt;a href=&quot;https://lists.apache.org/thread.html/r401e672505d0585818012a87640942083abed966e6d765f5b7313b3a%40%3Cdev.camel.apache.org%3E&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;the dev mailing list&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=onders&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;onders&quot;&gt;onders&lt;/a&gt; reported an issue using pollEnrich in combination with a REST request to upload files. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
from(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;direct:uploadFiles&quot;&lt;/span&gt;)
        .pollEnrich(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;file:{{shared-folder}}?include=.*.gz&amp;amp;delete=&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;true&lt;/span&gt;&amp;amp;sendEmptyMessageWhenIdle=&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;true&lt;/span&gt;&quot;&lt;/span&gt;)
        .choice()
          .when(body().isNull()).log(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;No files found.. skipping to send to S3&quot;&lt;/span&gt;)
          .otherwise().to(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;direct:toAwsS3&quot;&lt;/span&gt;)
        .endChoice();
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If the shared-folder contained no file, the empty event was sent, but when a file was then put in the folder, the empty event was still sent on the next rest request.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
